{{Infobox philosopher |region = [[Western philosophy]] |era = [[Contemporary philosophy|21st century Philosophy]] |color = |image = |name = '''Alejandro Barcenas Pardo''' |birth_date = |birth_place = |death_date = |death_place = |school_tradition = [[Renaissance philosophy]] | institutions = [[Texas State University]] |main_interests = [[political philosophy]], [[comparative philosophy]] | thesis_title = | thesis_url = | thesis_year = | doctoral_advisor = | doctoral_students = |notable_ideas = | spouse = | education = | alma_mater = [[University of Hawaii at Manoa]] |influences = [[Plato]], [[Machiavelli]], [[Hegel]] |influenced = |awards = |website = http://www.latinamericanhistory.net/index.html }}
'''Alejandro Barcenas Pardo''' is a Venezuelan [[philosopher]] and Assistant Professor of [[Philosophy at Texas State University]]. He is known for his expertise on [[Machiavelli]]'s thought.<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Menchaca-Bagnulo |first1=Ashleen |title=Alejandro Bárcenas: Machiavelli's Art of Politics. (Leiden: Brill Rodopi, 2015. Pp. i, 167.) |journal=[[The Review of Politics]] |date=Summer 2016 |volume=78 |issue=3 |pages=467–469 |doi=10.1017/S0034670516000383 |url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/review-of-politics/article/alejandrobarcenas-machiavellis-art-of-politics-leiden-brill-rodopi-2015-pp-i-167/75801C9081B476FCFACF918D8AABBC6C |accessdate=12 June 2018 |language=en |issn=0034-6705}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Landon |first1=William |title=Alejandro Barcenas. Machiavelli's Art of Politics |journal=[[Renaissance Quarterly]] |date=Spring 2017 |volume=70 |issue=1 |pages=300–301 |url=https://www.journals.uchicago.edu/action/captchaChallenge?redirectUri=%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1086%2F691877 |accessdate=12 June 2018 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Valle |first1=Marina Pérez del |title=A. Bárcenas, "Machiavelli's Art of Politics" |journal=[[Ingenium. Revista Electrónica de Pensamiento Moderno y Metodología en Historia de las Ideas]] |date=11 December 2017 |volume=11 |issue=0 |pages=311–315 |doi=10.5209/INGE.58314 |url=https://revistas.ucm.es/index.php/INGE/article/view/58314 |accessdate=12 June 2018 |language=es |issn=1989-3663}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Voegelin: Machiavelli in His Context |url=https://voegelinview.com/voegelin-machiavelli-in-his-context/ |website=[[VoegelinView]] |accessdate=12 June 2018 |date=22 January 2016}}</ref>
